cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper deals with medical image segmentation using deep learning techniques, specifically Gated Graph Neural Networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of learnable adjacency weighted matrix, which falls under the category of graph neural networks, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves the use of recurrent neural networks, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper involves the use of medical imaging, which falls under the category of Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) and Multimedia (cs.MM).
